    "Figure 2 provides an example of the feature extraction procedure of atom 2 in the Butyramide molecule considering interested radius of 1.",
    "In particular, this algorithm involves three stages:",
    "Initial Stage: Each atom in the molecule is assigned with a unique integer identifier which is generated by hashing a set of chemical properties. 2.",
    "Updating Stage: After initialization, each atom's identifier will be updated iteratively.",
    "Starting by radius r = 1: (a) An array will be formed by collecting the radius and the core atom's current identifier."
